OL,5,BALIENGby Connie, seven, Christ the King
OL,6,GPrimary School, Birmingham.            
OL,8,CIn the middle of the night I was woken 
OL,9,Cup by a strange, funny noise. I looked 
OL,10,Cout of my bedroom window.              
OL,12,CI saw bright lights like a rainbow, in 
OL,13,Cthe middle was an alien. He was pink   
OL,14,Cwith blue spots.                       
OL,16,CHe got a ladder up to my bedroom window
OL,17,Cand gave me a birthday present. Then he
OL,18,Cflew off into the stars.               
